         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">2/8/87. ¶  ¶ Kindly tell me, dear Professor Kirk, what is the greatest height that any Veronica in N.Z. does attain under the most favorable circumstances and at its advanced age. ¶  ¶ I send you now ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.08.02b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Kirk</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">LS/2/90/309 (87/353) inward letters, Secretary for Crown Lands (Forests and Agricultural Branch), National Archives of New Zealand, Wellington.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">2/8/87.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Kindly tell me, dear Professor Kirk, what is the greatest height that any <name key="Veronica">Veronica</name> in N.Z. does attain under the most favorable circumstances and at its advanced age.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I send you now some seeds of <name key="Eucalyptus%20tereticornis">Eucalyptus tereticornis</name>, which yields excellent timber, and is easier and quicker reared than E. marginata.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I am so glad to learn that you are now getting quite well again. Seeds of Euc. Gunnii and E. rostrata are now being purposely collected for you, in quantities indicated by you as required.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See T. Kirk to M, 8 June 1887.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20Gunnii">Eucalyptus Gunnii</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20marginata">Eucalyptus marginata</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20rostrata">Eucalyptus rostrata</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20tereticornis">Eucalyptus tereticornis</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Veronica">Veronica</name>
            </p>
